<br>
Although the magician POP armor has several effects that improve our ability to nuke (casting haste on boots, spell damage focus on gloves, flowing thought on the bracer), none of it really improves magicians as a &quot;pet class&quot;.  <br>
<br>
The effect could be much like the VT focus gloves, but would be obtainiable in POP zones.  They could even add a variety effects distributed over the various pieces of armor.<br>
<br>
